  <entry>
    <title>怎样写一个可以自动推导依赖的 makefile ？</title>
    <link href="/2021/05/02/makefile/"/>
    <url>/2021/05/02/makefile/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>本文假设读者对 makefile 有足够多的了解，所以不对一些基础内容作过多的解释。</p></blockquote><h2 id="为什么需要自动推导依赖？"><a href="#为什么需要自动推导依赖？" class="headerlink" title="为什么需要自动推导依赖？"></a>为什么需要自动推导依赖？</h2><p>我们知道，一个 c 文件可能会依赖很多头文件。但是在使用模式匹配的时候，往往是不会在规则后加上头文件的。一般的后缀规则大致都长这个样：</p><figure class="highlight makefile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs makefile">%.o : %.c<br><span class="hljs-variable">$(CC)</span> -o <span class="hljs-variable">$@</span> -c <span class="hljs-variable">$^</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这样会导致一些问题，<strong>头文件发生了变动，重新 make 后根本不会触发编译</strong>。为什么会这样？看看上面的模式匹配就可以知道，目标文件只依赖 c 文件。</p><p>可能有人会想，把所有的头文件都当作依赖：</p><figure class="highlight makefile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs makefile">%.o : %.c 1.h 2.h 3.h ...<br><span class="hljs-variable">$(CC)</span> -o <span class="hljs-variable">$@</span> -c <span class="hljs-variable">$^</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这样的问题会变得更加严重！！！</p><ul><li>把所有的头文件都加上，当项目中的头文件数目巨大时，makefile 将难以维护</li><li>头文件作为依赖条件出现于每个目标对应的规则中</li><li>当头文件改动，任何源文件都需要被重新编译，这会非常的低效</li></ul><p>那么，真正高效的 makefile 应该是啥样的？可能至少得包含以下的所有方面吧。🐶</p><ul><li>自动生成目标的依赖，包括头文件和源文件</li><li>头文件改动后，只会重新编译依赖该头文件的目标文件</li></ul><p>来康康吧。🐶</p><h2 id="gcc-MM-E-和-sed"><a href="#gcc-MM-E-和-sed" class="headerlink" title="gcc -MM -E 和 sed"></a><code>gcc -MM -E</code> 和 <code>sed</code></h2><p><code>gcc -MM -E</code> 可以输出目标文件的依赖，包括头文件。配合 <code>sed</code> 使用，可以生成我们需要的依赖格式。</p><p>比如，可能有下面的程序：</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-comment">/*main.c*/</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-meta-string">&quot;const.h&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-meta-string">&quot;lib.h&quot;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>        print();<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d\n&quot;</span>, MAX_NUM);<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-comment">/*lib.h*/</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">print</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span>;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-comment">/*lib.c*/</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-meta-string">&quot;lib.h&quot;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">print</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;hello\n&quot;</span>);<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-comment">/*const.h*/</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-meta-keyword">define</span> MAX_NUM 99</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用 <code>gcc -MM -E</code> 可以得到：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">main.o: main.c const.h lib.h<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>同样，对于 lib.c 而言，就有下面的结果了：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">lib.o: lib.c lib.h<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可以看到，使用 <code>gcc -MM -E</code> 可以很清楚的通过源文件知道目标文件所对应的依赖，无论是头文件还是源文件。</p><p>那么，为什么需要使用 <code>sed</code> 呢？</p><p>为了使项目文件尽可能地整洁，需要将所有生成的目标文件单独放在同一个文件夹下，比如 <code>objs</code> 。通过使用 <code>sed</code> 处理 <code>gcc</code> 输出的字符串，来得到我们想要的结果，比如使用 <code>gcc -MM -E lib.c | sed &#39;s,\(.*\)\.o[ :]*,objs/\1.o : ,g&#39;</code> 可以得到：</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c">objs/lib.o : lib.c lib.h<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>sed</code> 是一个很强大的处理文本的工具，具体怎么使用，还是看帮助文档吧。</p><h2 id="include"><a href="#include" class="headerlink" title="include"></a><code>include</code></h2><p>makefile 中的 <code>include</code> 和 C 语言中的差不太多。就是将其他文件的内容搬入当前文件中。需要注意的是 make 会在前目录或者指定目录搜索文件，对于搜索的结果的不同也有不同的处理方式：</p><ul><li>搜索成功：将文件内容搬入当前 makefile 文件中</li><li>搜索失败：产生警告<ul><li>以文件名作为目标，查找并执行对应的规则</li><li>当文件名对应的规则不存在时，最终产生错误</li></ul></li></ul><p>使用 <code>-include</code> 不但关闭了 <code>include</code> 发出的警告，同时关闭了错误；当错误发生时，make 将会忽略这些错误。 </p><p><code>include</code> 和我们的方案有什么联系呢？</p><p>使用 <code>gcc -MM -E</code> 生成的依赖，我们会把它保存在一个文件中，这个文件不是 makefile ，所以需要使用 <code>include</code> 将其引进 makefile 。</p><p>方案中，<code>gcc -MM -E</code> 生成的每一个依赖都会保存在 deps 文件夹下的 *.dep 文件中。通过 <code>include</code> 相关 dep 文件，来将依赖添加到 makefile 中。</p><h2 id="最终方案"><a href="#最终方案" class="headerlink" title="最终方案"></a>最终方案</h2><figure class="highlight makefile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs makefile">.PHONY : all clean rebuild<br><br>CC := gcc<br>RM := rm -fr<br>MKDIR := mkdir<br><br>DIR_DEPS := deps<br>DIR_OBJS := objs<br>DIR_EXES := exes<br><br>DIRS := <span class="hljs-variable">$(DIR_DEPS)</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$(DIR_OBJS)</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$(DIR_EXES)</span><br><br>EXE := target<br>EXE := <span class="hljs-variable">$(<span class="hljs-built_in">addprefix</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$(DIR_EXES)</span>/,<span class="hljs-variable">$(EXE)</span>)</span><br><br>SRCS := <span class="hljs-variable">$(<span class="hljs-built_in">wildcard</span> *.c)</span><br>OBJS := $(SRCS:.c=.o)<br>OBJS := <span class="hljs-variable">$(<span class="hljs-built_in">addprefix</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$(DIR_OBJS)</span>/,<span class="hljs-variable">$(OBJS)</span>)</span><br>DEPS := $(SRCS:.c=.dep)<br>DEPS := <span class="hljs-variable">$(<span class="hljs-built_in">addprefix</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$(DIR_DEPS)</span>/,<span class="hljs-variable">$(DEPS)</span>)</span><br><br>all : <span class="hljs-variable">$(DIR_OBJS)</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$(DIR_EXES)</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$(EXE)</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 避免在 make 除 all 和默认目标外，也会执行 include 这个不必要的操作</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">ifeq</span> (<span class="hljs-string">&quot;<span class="hljs-variable">$(MAKECMDGOALS)</span>&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;all&quot;</span>)<br><span class="hljs-keyword">-include</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$(DEPS)</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">endif</span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">ifeq</span> (<span class="hljs-string">&quot;<span class="hljs-variable">$(MAKECMDGOALS)</span>&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span>)<br><span class="hljs-keyword">-include</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$(DEPS)</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">endif</span><br><br><span class="hljs-variable">$(EXE)</span> : <span class="hljs-variable">$(OBJS)</span><br>        <span class="hljs-variable">$(CC)</span> -o <span class="hljs-variable">$@</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$^</span><br><br><span class="hljs-variable">$(DIR_OBJS)</span>/%.o : %.c<br>        <span class="hljs-variable">$(CC)</span> -o <span class="hljs-variable">$@</span> -c <span class="hljs-variable">$(<span class="hljs-built_in">filter</span> %.c,<span class="hljs-variable">$^</span>)</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 避免因为文件夹时间戳更新而重复生成 .dep 文件</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">ifeq</span> (<span class="hljs-string">&quot;$(wildcard <span class="hljs-variable">$(DIR_DEPS)</span>)&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span>)<br><span class="hljs-variable">$(DIR_DEPS)</span>/%.dep : <span class="hljs-variable">$(DIR_DEPS)</span> %.c<br><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span><br><span class="hljs-variable">$(DIR_DEPS)</span>/%.dep : %.c<br><span class="hljs-keyword">endif</span><br>        @set -e;\<br>        <span class="hljs-variable">$(CC)</span> -MM -E <span class="hljs-variable">$(<span class="hljs-built_in">filter</span> %.c,<span class="hljs-variable">$^</span>)</span> | sed &#x27;s,\(.*\)\.o[ :]*,objs/\1.o <span class="hljs-variable">$@</span> : ,g&#x27; &gt; <span class="hljs-variable">$@</span><br><br><span class="hljs-variable">$(DIRS)</span> :<br>        <span class="hljs-variable">$(MKDIR)</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$@</span><br><br>clean :<br>        <span class="hljs-variable">$(RM)</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$(DIRS)</span><br><br>rebuild :<br>        <span class="hljs-variable">$(MAKE)</span> clean<br>        <span class="hljs-variable">$(MAKE)</span> all<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
